---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Web Scraping & Automation Services | Empower VA Services">
  <style>
    /* New Colour Palette */
    .bg-pale-purple {
        background-color: #f9edf8;
    }

    .bg-dark-purple {
        background-color: #972092;
    }

    .text-pink {
        color: #e3197e;
    }

    .bg-pink {
        background-color: #e3197e;
    }

    .hover-bg-pink-dark:hover {
        background-color: #c4146a;
    }

    .border-pink {
        border-color: #e3197e;
    }

    .bg-lavender {
        background-color: #E6E6FA;
    }

    .hover-bg-lavender-dark:hover {
        background-color: #D8BFD8;
    }

    .accordion-content {
        max-height: 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        transition: max-height 0.3s ease-out;
    }
  </style>

  <div class="bg-[#f9edf8] dark:bg-slate-900 min-h-screen">
    <header class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 shadow-md">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-4 text-center">
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#e3197e]">Empower Virtual Assistant Services - Web Scraping & Automation</h1>
            <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-2">Intelligent Data Solutions Powered by Python</h2>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container mx-auto px-6 py-12">

        <section class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                At Empower Virtual Assistant Services, we specialise in transforming time-consuming manual tasks into streamlined, automated processes. Leveraging advanced technology, we provide bespoke solutions for both intelligent web data collection and efficient Google Workspace automation.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-16 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-center">
                <div class="md:col-span-1 flex justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-32 h-32 text-[#e3197e]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path>
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-2">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#e3197e]">What is Web Scraping?</h3>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Web scraping is the automated process of collecting publicly available information from websites. Instead of manually copying and pasting, our sophisticated tools can systematically extract specific data points, lists, or content, converting them into structured, usable formats like Google Sheets or CSV files.</p>
                    <div class="mt-6 bg-[#f9edf8] dark:bg-slate-700 p-4 rounded-lg">
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-[#e3197e] flex items-center">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                            </svg>
                            How Python Powers Your Efficiency
                        </h4>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Utilising powerful Python programming, we develop custom tools tailored to your unique data needs. This allows us to build robust, precise, and efficient automated solutions that go beyond standard off-the-shelf software.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-16">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#e3197e] text-center mb-8">Practical Use Examples for Your Business</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <button class="accordion-header w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 text-left font-semibold text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-white">
                        <span>Market Research & Competitor Analysis</span>
                        <svg class="accordion-icon w-6 h-6 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion-content px-5 pb-5 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                        <p><strong>Scenario:</strong> You need to understand competitor service offerings, features, or public pricing structures.<br><strong>Our Solution:</strong> We automate the collection of this data from their websites, organising it in a Google Sheet for easy comparison and strategic insights.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <button class="accordion-header w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 text-left font-semibold text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-white">
                        <span>Public Lead Generation & Directory Compilation</span>
                        <svg class="accordion-icon w-6 h-6 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion-content px-5 pb-5 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                        <p><strong>Scenario:</strong> You’re building a list of potential clients from publicly accessible directories.<br><strong>Our Solution:</strong> Systematically extract business names, public contact details, or company descriptions into a clean CSV or Google Sheet for targeted outreach (adhering strictly to all data privacy regulations like GDPR).</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <button class="accordion-header w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 text-left font-semibold text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-white">
                        <span>Content Research & Curation</span>
                        <svg class="accordion-icon w-6 h-6 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion-content px-5 pb-5 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                        <p><strong>Scenario:</strong> You need to gather information or statistics from multiple pages of specific blogs or industry reports.<br><strong>Our Solution:</strong> Automate the extraction of relevant text, headings, or summaries, delivering curated content directly to a Google Doc or Sheet for your review.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <button class="accordion-header w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 text-left font-semibold text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-white">
                        <span>Reputation & Review Monitoring</span>
                        <svg class="accordion-icon w-6 h-6 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion-content px-5 pb-5 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                        <p><strong>Scenario:</strong> You want to keep track of new public reviews for your business (or a competitor) on a specific directory site.<br><strong>Our Solution:</strong> Our script can visit the page periodically, extract new reviews, and log them in a spreadsheet. Using Apps Script, we can even set it to email you an alert whenever a new review is found.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <button class="accordion-header w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 text-left font-semibold text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-white">
                        <span>Job Board Monitoring</span>
                        <svg class="accordion-icon w-6 h-6 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion-content px-5 pb-5 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                        <p><strong>Scenario:</strong> You're a freelancer who manually checks a specific job board every day for new projects.<br><strong>Our Solution:</strong> We build a tool that automatically scrapes the board for new listings matching your keywords (e.g., "Graphic Design," "VA") and compiles them into a daily digest in a Google Sheet, saving you hours of searching.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-16 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#e3197e] text-center mb-6">Leveraging Your Existing Data: Our API Integration Expertise</h3>
            <p class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">If you already have access to an API (Application Programming Interface), that is the ideal and most reliable method for data retrieval. Our Python expertise extends beyond web scraping to seamlessly integrate with these official data channels.</p>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center">
                <div class="bg-[#f9edf8] dark:bg-slate-700 p-6 rounded-lg">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-[#e3197e]">API Connectivity</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-2">We connect directly to your APIs, handle authentication, and securely fetch raw data.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-[#f9edf8] dark:bg-slate-700 p-6 rounded-lg">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-[#e3197e]">Data Transformation</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-2">We process, clean, and restructure complex data, ensuring it’s perfectly formatted for your needs.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-[#f9edf8] dark:bg-slate-700 p-6 rounded-lg">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-[#e3197e]">Automated Delivery</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-2">Your valuable API data can be automatically pushed into Google Sheets, databases, or other business systems.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-16">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#e3197e] text-center mb-8">Important Considerations & Our Ethical Approach</h3>
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-[#972092] text-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-inner text-gray-800 space-y-4">
                <p><strong class="text-white">Publicly Available Data Only:</strong> We focus strictly on data that is publicly accessible without requiring logins or bypassing security measures.</p>
                <p><strong class="text-white">Ethical & Legal Compliance:</strong> We adhere rigorously to all relevant data protection regulations, including GDPR. We respect website Terms of Service and do not violate copyright.</p>
                <p><strong class="text-white">Website Specificity:</strong> Each custom web scraping solution is designed for one specific website. Extracting data from multiple distinct platforms will require separate, tailored solutions.</p>
                <p><strong class="text-white">API Preference:</strong> For platforms that offer official APIs, we strongly advocate for and utilise these sanctioned channels as they provide the most reliable and ethical method of data retrieval.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-20 bg-[#e3197e] text-white text-center p-12 rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold">Ready to Harness Your Data?</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">Once your valuable data is extracted and organised, its potential is limitless. We can help you integrate it into Google Workspace, enhance your workflows with Apps Script, or connect it to other business applications. Stop wasting time on manual data collection and start making informed decisions.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-block bg-[#E6E6FA] text-gray-800 font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:bg-[#D8BFD8] transition-colors text-lg">
                Contact Us Today
            </a>
        </section>
    </main>
  </div>

  <script>
    // Simple Accordion Script
    document.querySelectorAll('.accordion-header').forEach(button => {
        button.addEventListener('click', () => {
            const accordionContent = button.nextElementSibling;
            const accordionIcon = button.querySelector('.accordion-icon');

            button.classList.toggle('active');

            if (button.classList.contains('active')) {
                if (accordionContent) accordionContent.style.maxHeight = accordionContent.scrollHeight + 'px';
                if (accordionIcon) accordionIcon.style.transform = 'rotate(180deg)';
            } else {
                if (accordionContent) accordionContent.style.maxHeight = '0';
                if (accordionIcon) accordionIcon.style.transform = 'rotate(0deg)';
            }
        });
    });
  </script>
</Layout>
